Okular environment

Also useful for a lot of KDE applications

Use:
Source 'bashrc' from your project's folder
  $ cd /project/source
  $ source /dotfiles/environment/okular/bashrc

Tip: Create a symbolic link to the file

Create a build directory
  $ mkdir build

Inside that, run 'cmake'
  $ cd build
  $ cmake ..

Build and install
  $ make
  $ make install

Rebuild KDE configuration cache
  $ kbuildsycoca4

Run
  $ okular
